name: Google Bard
description: Bard is an early experiment by Google that allows users to collaborate with generative AI to boost productivity, accelerate ideas, and fuel curiosity. Powered by a research large language model (LLM), Bard assists users by generating responses to prompts, outlining blog posts, providing tips, and explaining complex concepts in simple terms. As an experiment, Bard may sometimes produce inaccurate or biased information, but it also offers multiple drafts of responses for users to choose from. Google is rolling out access to Bard in the U.S. and the U.K., with plans to expand to more countries and languages over time.

name: Adobe Firefly
description: Adobe Firefly is a family of creative generative AI models designed to enhance the creative process for artists, designers, and creators. It allows users to generate extraordinary content using everyday language and offers potential applications in digital imaging, photography, illustration, graphic design, video, marketing, social media, and 3D modeling. Firefly aims to provide practical advantages to creators, streamline workflows, and offer AI tools made specifically for creative needs. Adobe is committed to developing Firefly responsibly, ensuring transparency and accountability in generative AI.

name: Bing Create
description: The Microsoft Bing Image Creator is a tool that uses AI to generate images based on words and text. It allows users to redeem Rewards points for boosts to speed up the image generation process. It is currently available in some regions and the team is working to bring it to more regions. It is powered by an advanced version of DALLE-2

name: Get Floor Plan
description: Getfloorplan is a service that provides 2D, 3D floor plans and 360° virtual tours to boost sales in real estate. It uses AI to create high quality materials quickly and at a low cost, and provides customers with a full pack of marketing materials. The service also offers a money-back guarantee if customers are unhappy with the result.

name: Hypertype
description: Hypertype is an AI-powered engine that helps teams find the most relevant information from emails and documents in real-time. It uses a Chrome extension to integrate directly with Gmail and allows users to upload their internal FAQs and documents. It extracts the most relevant context from emails and FAQs and automatically matches and fetches the best replies. Hyperbrain™ also automatically creates new knowledge and insights for teams.

name: Magic Studio
description: Aarzoo Inc. provides a suite of tools to help create amazing product photos, stunning profile pictures, pictures with words, and remove unwanted things and backgrounds. It also offers the ability to enlarge pictures without losing quality and an FAQ section. Additionally, it has an affiliate program that rewards customers with 25% for referring customers.

name: nameSnack
description: nameSnack is a free business name generator that allows users to create unique and memorable names for their brand. It uses machine learning, keyword combining and other proprietary techniques to generate names for websites, startups, apps, shops, stores, restaurants, podcasts, products, brands, Etsy shops, Shopify stores, blogs, and more. nameSnack also provides users with a domain name search, allowing them to instantly discover what domains are available. Additionally, users can generate a beautiful logo for their brand with a few clicks.

name: Coda AI
description: Coda AI provides a platform for businesses and individuals to streamline their workflow processes. It allows users to consolidate their tool stack, save money with its pricing_model, and access product updates, case studies, and solutions. Additionally, the platform offers tutorials, webinars, and a help center to help users get started. The Coda AI limited alpha is available by signing up on the waitlist to gain access to the platform's AI capabilities.

It provides a glossary feature to store all extracted terms and definitions and a Term Page to allow for in-depth comprehension of relevant terms.

It has features such as personalisation, email/letter mode, mark and grade mode, lesson plan mode, resource from lesson plan mode, quiz mode, brainstorm mode, and a time saved counter.

It can answer in over 20+ languages and provides an unlimited free tier for those who self-host. The platform also provides summarization and codebase change options to help speed up code review, planning, and other tasks.

It is available on Chrome and Firefox and collects usage data to complete prompts. It also sends the contents of prompts to OpenAI, which does not keep data for longer than 30 days.

It offers 20+ templates, GPT-3 model support, and the ability to save important documents. It also provides social media tips and tricks, SEO-friendly headlines, titles, meta descriptions and keywords, and effortless marketing campaigns and ads copy. description: Chatpad AI is a free and open source chat user-interface that focuses on privacy and providing the best user experience possible. It allows users to download a desktop app, as well as manage their data, such as exporting and importing data, as well as deleting data.

name: ChatGPT Personality Selector
description: The ChatGPT Personality Selector is a Google Chrome extension that allows users to customize their chatbot experience by selecting from an extensive list of personalities. The extension also offers special personalities such as the NetEnabled ChatGPT, which can connect to the internet and perform searches to provide users with up-to-date information. Additionally, the extension offers keyword interception control and the chatgpt_extensions tool, which allows users to condition the chatbot for specific applications and tasks. The full source code of the ChatGPT Personality Selector is open source under the MIT license.

description: eCold.ai is an AI powered tool for automating cold email personalization. It allows users to quickly generate 100s of personalized lines in seconds and integrates with the most popular cold email tools. It is 6X cheaper than hiring a VA and provides increased reply rates.

It features a machine learning model that automatically recommends highlights, a templated video generator, and options to post clips on social media, embed them on websites, or link them on emails and SMS. Qlip offers plans with varying amounts of storage space and upload time, with the first hour of upload being free.

It allows users to create online summary documents, and add comments, links, images, and more. It also features an AI-generated notes tool, auto-highlighting, audio player, sharing and collaboration capabilities, and unlimited storage. Users can also listen to their summaries on the go, and organize content summaries in their lifelong library. It is available for a 7-day free trial, with a monthly subscription fee after that. Special student pricing is also available.

name: Scrip AI
description: Scrip AI tool provides a 10X faster way to write short video scripts for Instagram. It allows users to create scripts for videos that are 30-60 seconds in length in only 1 minute. It is free to use and does not require a credit card or login.

Ariana also offers support for students, parents, work, freelancers, and creatives. The service is offered with a monthly or yearly subscription, with a free trial available and no credit card required. Users can also contact Timworks for further help.

name: Norby AI

Users simply create an account, copy-paste a snippet of code onto their website, and copy-paste their FAQs or documents onto the dashboard. The chatbot is then ready to use.

It features local AI for Command Prediction and cloud-based AI for AI Command Search. Warp AI is free to use during the beta period and includes a limit of 100 requests per user per day.

It connects all relevant links and files, provides instant, bite-sized answers with auto-generated summaries, and is secure and GDPR compliant.

Collie also offers a private embedded file search for select users in beta.

A $20 monthly donation is requested of those who want to test Khanmigo.

It is free to use, and supports websites such as Yahoo!, PubMed, PMC, NewsPicks, Github, Nikkei, Bing, Google Patents. No ChatGPT/OpenAI account is required.

It works best with the Relume Library Figma Kit and is compatible with Figma & Webflow. It has a range of pricing plans and is also available to try for free with a 2,000 word limit.

It features a Text-to-Speech feature, pre-built video templates, a hassle-free online video editor, and a diverse cast of over 100 fully licensed AI avatars. Additionally, it supports multi-language Text-to-Speech and the ability to create custom avatars. Finally, it has a 3D Digital Human feature for a more immersive experience.

name: Dime A Dozen
description: Dimeadozen is an AI-powered tool that helps to validate business ideas in seconds. It provides market research, launch and scale, and raise capital insights for businesses. It also offers competitive analysis, business overviews, elevator pitches, and potential risks for businesses. Additionally, it provides users with SEO copy, website copy, and investor pitches.

It allows users to add backgrounds to product images and turn them into professional-looking photos with zero quality loss. It is deeply integrated with Shopify and allows users to generate unlimited product photo images for free, or pay only for the images they like. description: Promptitude is an AI NLP tool that helps developers easily integrate GPT features into their SaaS and mobile apps. It also offers a library of ready-to-use GPT prompts and the ability to collect user feedback to improve prompts.

description: ElliSense is an artificial intelligence-powered application that provides up-to-date market sentiment analysis for a variety of assets, including stocks, cryptocurrencies, and foreign currencies. It collects data from a variety of sources and digests them to provide clear market insights with a Social Sentiment Index. It also offers advanced charting to view historical sentiment and spot market mood highlights. ElliSense has partnered with major financial information and exchange platforms to bring the tool to the world’s top traders and financial institutions.

description: Spacely AI is a tool that helps people create their dream living space. It provides interior design inspiration and allows users to upload images and choose a style and room type. It will also provide interior design images for implementation, along with a furniture list and color scheme for contractors.

It also includes a for loop creative project that displays all the numbers from 1-100 except for one number, with the user needing to input the missing number in order to exit the loop. The MIDI export titling has been changed so that the MIDI filename is now set to track_name.

It enables users to turn any text prompt into a visually stunning image, explore a wide range of styles and templates, and use advanced photo editing tools. MajorGen also provides users with up to 5 different options to choose from, and the resumes and cover letters can be downloaded as PDF or Word documents.

It offers a free plan with limited features and a premium plan with more benefits. The service costs 0.01 EUR for each processed response offered to customers. It can answer questions and provide information on any topic, give personalized recommendations, help with language translation, and more. It comes with real-time voice changer, unlimited audio & sound effects, studio-quality voice recorder, text to speech, and speech to text. FineVoice also supports multitrack recording, audio extraction, audio file voice changing, and sound effects. It is suitable for online meetings, lectures and meetings, live streams, podcast creation, video production, and gaming.

It helps users generate unique compositions, infinite variations, and professionally looking designs in just a minute. It helps marketers, business owners, content writers, and e-commerce managers create visually engaging ads that convert better and faster.

It provides access to powerful artificial intelligence, Amazon synchronization, advanced SEO features, hosting and installation of the solution, and more. It also includes a complete dashboard to manage SEO, automatic import of products and synchronization of prices and availability. The tool uses user's contact details and job description to match their skills and experience and generate a custom cover letter. The process is fast and easy and can help users get more interviews.

name: Roshi

The website also offers royalty free music and the user is granted a perpetual license for usage of the soundtracks.

It supports multiple languages, and can also work with accents from other countries. It allows users to export timelines for manual editing, and also provides a range of other tools and services such as podcast transcription, podcast mixing, background noise remover, podcast name generator, podcast audit, podcast question generator, and episode title generator.

name: Illustroke

It uses AI-algorithm to generate listing content and competitor insights to apply relevant and potential keywords. It also offers an Amazon Copywriter to help sellers generate content and the ability to continuously optimize listings in order to drive sales. CopyMonkey's AI-powered technology is proven by Amazon experts and is used by more than 1000 sellers.

name: Imaiger

Markopolo also helps marketers automate daily actions, use targeting AI to generate custom audience presets, and get a holistic overview of all the metrics in one dashboard.

name: Bing

It consolidates reliable sources across the web to give summarized answers and allows users to ask follow-up questions in the chat experience. Microsoft is committed to responsible AI and has taken steps to ensure the tool is used responsibly. Users can access the new Bing by joining the waitlist and then accessing it at Bing.com.

It features seo optimized content generation, copywriting, digital ads, emails, image and video editors, link shortener, approval workflow, and one-click publishing capabilities. It also provides a bulk upload option. Postly helps marketers and businesses to boost marketing campaigns, engagement, and conversions.

It helps teams automate data enrichment, create personalized emails, summarize customer requests and use it in automated replies, generate content that passes AI-generated text checks., social media posts and profiles, classify customer requests and tickets, and create engaging LinkedIn ads.

It uses deep learning techniques such as transformer networks to generate human-like text and answer questions about crypto and blockchain. It can help with programming and development tasks, blockchain analytics, risk management, AI trading, and more. In addition, the Chatmates are powered by Open AI GPT-3, and are aware of their own personalities and conversation styles. A paid subscription is required to chat with more than 10 lines.

It provides features such as real-time transcription and tagging, personalized meeting templates, audio to text, smart memos, world-class editors, insight management, search, and download and share capabilities. It also integrates with popular platforms such as Zoom, Google Meet, Webex, and Microsoft Teams.

Ideal for businesses and individuals, Piggy Magic offers a user-friendly, time-saving solution for creating impactful content.

Cleo can also access the web for answers and information, making it an invaluable source of information and support. With its powerful AI capabilities, Cleo can provide personalized advice and guidance, helping to make tedious tasks easier and faster

The tool supports features such as code generation, code refactoring, and code debugging, as well as intelligent code completion. It also allows users to share their snippets with their team, and generate natural language explanations of code to improve readability. Additionally, the tool offers three different subscription plans to suit different user needs.

Users should exercise caution when using this extension, and should not use it on pages with private information.

description: The artificial intelligence tool To Teach provides teachers with personalized materials and exercises tailored to the interests and needs of their students. It offers both free and paid plans which include printable and digital materials, ready-to-teach worksheets, and the ability to create exercises, lesson plans, and use gamification options. It eliminates the need for costly manual labor while ensuring that calls are handled in a consistent and professional manner. It features automated call answering, call routing, call logging, affordable pricing, on-the-go account management, and customer service.

name: Obituary Writer

It provides users with the ability to fill in the required fields (full name, date of birth, place of birth, date of passing, place of passing, family members, personal details, and additional details) to create a customized obituary. Additionally, the tool offers an example obituary to help users get started. It also provides resources and a marketplace to help users plan ahead and manage their losses.

name: Extractify
description: This tool allows video creators to generate Twitter and LinkedIn content from their youtube videos. If a Youtube creator wants to find new audience on twitter or LinkedIn, they can use their videos to generate content for these platforms efficiently.

It supports various types of documents, including research papers, books, newspapers, study guides, and manuals. Users can upload files and ask questions to their personalized chatbot, with direct citations pulled from the document to support the answer. It also offers cloud storage with strict security measures in place. Filechat offers a free trial and two subscription plans with access to all new features.

name: Humata
description: Upload documents and then ask it questions. This tool provides an easy way to quickly summarize long papers, get instant answers to difficult questions, and write papers 10X faster. It enables users to quickly discover new insights, generate detailed insights, and simplify complex technical papers.

name: Fini
description: Fini is an AI chat tool that helps growth teams at PLG companies to identify reasons for churn and deliver personalized experiences to retain existing customers. It offers features such as tone and character configuration, seamless human routing, multi-channel approach, feedback learning, and more. It also provides key metrics such as retention uplift, revenue/user uplift, activation uplift, and integration time. Additionally, it offers integrations with Intercom, Slack, and Discord and is trusted by data-driven tech companies around the world.

name: InfraNodus
description: InfraNodus is an AI-powered text network visualization tool that helps to generate insight and new ideas. It can represent any text as a network and identify and visualize the main ideas, relations between them, and blind spots. It uses natural language processing algorithms and GPT-3 AI to generate highly relevant queries to help come up with interesting ideas, facts, and research questions. It has data import and export capabilities, text mining and sentiment analysis, network analysis and visualization, multilingual support, and is private by default. It also has a mindmap and knowledge graph feature, and an API. It is an open-source, “organic” software developed without external funds or investors.

name: Stable Attribution
description: The Stable Attribution tool allows people to identify the creators of images that have been used to train an AI. It works by uploading an image generated by Stable Diffusion and will identify the human-made source images and the people who made them. It also allows users to share the attribution link of the creator if known.

name: Chatbase
description: Chatbase is a tool that allows users to create an AI chatbot trained on their data. Users can upload a PDF document which the chatbot will use to answer any questions about the content of the document. The character limit for the document is 1.2M characters, and soon users will be able to submit a link to their website for the chatbot to scrape the text from.

name: ProfilePicture.AI
description: Postcraft's Free PFP Maker is an online tool that allows users to create custom profile pictures for their social media accounts. It allows users to upload a photo and then the tool will automatically remove the background and generate hundreds of unique profile pictures. It is perfect for creating profile pictures for Instagram, Twitter, Facebook, TikTok, Snapchat, YouTube, and more. The tool is free and no sign up is required.

name: GPTForMe
description: GPTfor.me is a tool that allows users to upload their own content to use as context for GPT-3. This allows users to ask GPT-3 about topics it may not know about. The tool uses a semantic search technique with OpenAI embeddings to create embeddings for both the uploaded content and the prompt. These embeddings are then used to calculate the most relevant content to submit to GPT-3 as context, which helps GPT-3 generate more accurate responses. This technique can be useful for a range of use cases, such as interacting with interesting content, helping students learn faster, answering questions about internal documents, teaching customers about products, and summarizing key thoughts from a conference.

name: FederAI
description: FederAI is an AI-powered content platform designed to help people grow their Twitter audience quickly and efficiently. It provides personalized content suggestions, viral tweet ideas, and tools to engage with the right audience. It also includes built-in AI, analytics, thread writer and scheduling tools, so users don't need to use multiple apps to manage their social media.

name: PowerMode
description: Help founders ideate and pitch your next startup, with the help of AI!

name: ogen.ai
description: The above tool is an AI-powered tool which can convert links into OG Image/Cover Photo using ChatGPT and Stable Diffusion. It can generate an image based on the input link.

name: Summate.it

name: MusicLM
description: The MusicLM tool is a model for generating high-fidelity music from text descriptions. The model is a hierarchical sequence-to-sequence modeling task that generates music at 24 kHz that remains consistent over several minutes. The tool can condition the generated music on both text and melody, allowing it to transform whistled and hummed melodies according to the style described in a text caption. The tool is also capable of generating music from painting descriptions, instruments, genres, musician experience levels, places, and epochs. Additionally, the tool is able to generate diverse versions of the same text prompt and the same semantic tokens.

name: HoustonAI
description: HoustonAI is an experiment to build an automated support bot (documentation) to assist Astro users. It is powered by GPT-3, LangChain, and the Astro documentation website.

name: ProjectAi
description: Project Ai is a research project that uses AI mechanisms to provide students with tools to improve their writing, summarization and outlining, as well as creating presentations and learning/studying resources such as flashcards. Users can enter their input and receive a response that can be copied/pasted or exported to supported platforms. It's build for Apple iOs.

name: Daily Zaps
description: Daily Zaps is a website that provides users with the latest news and breakthroughs in artificial intelligence (AI). It features articles, chatbot and virtual assistant apps, AI apps and tools directories, text-to-speech, text-to-video, AI detection/plagiarism detection, and AI startup news. Plus, it offers a wide range of cool AI apps and resources.

name: MidJourney Styles & Keywords
description: A reference containing Styles and Keywords that you can use with MidJourney AI. There are also pages showing resolution comparison, image weights, and much more!

name: Scalenut
description: Scalenut is an AI-powered content marketing platform that helps businesses plan, research, create, and optimize content. It features tools such as Cruise Mode, which creates SEO blogs in five minutes, AI Copywriting for creating persuasive copy, and SEO Hub for optimizing content with real-time feedback. Additionally, its integrations with other marketing apps make it easier to manage content across multiple platforms.

name: Switchboard Canvas
description: Switchboard Canvas is a media toolkit for digital creators, marketers, and automation gurus that allows users to automate image production using the API, or no-code tools like Zapier or Pabbly Connect. It also features a Template Designer to quickly create templates, as well as Tweet to Image and Twitter Headers. Users can also upload images and fonts, as well as translate text on the fly.

name: DocuChat
description: DocuChat is a GPT-3 powered chatbot service that allows users to upload documents, such as books, notes, essays, contracts, and guides, and ask questions in natural language to get answers from them. Users can create their own private or public chatbot, share them with friends, and get accurate answers from large bodies of text. The service also enables teams to train, onboard, and support employees with chatbots fed with company documents, and to make learning more convenient and engaging by uploading how-to resources, course materials, and notes.

name: MOVE Ai
description: Move.ai enables creators to bring motion into digital worlds at scale by using patented artificial intelligence software to extract high fidelity motion from any video. The company empowers creativity and digital self expression by providing enablement tools to create content for digital environments. They also offer motion licensing services.

name: WellSaid Labs
description: WellSaid is an AI text-to-speech tool that allows users to create realistic, natural sounding voiceovers from text. It provides a range of voice avatars and helps teams collaborate on projects, allowing for faster production times. It is suitable for enterprises and can be used for various applications, such as audio books, marketing, customer support, and more.

name: ValidatorAI
description: ValidatorAI.com is a free AI business validator tool that allows users to input their startup idea and receive objective feedback and criticism from an AI. The tool provides detailed feedback regarding market opportunity, legal issues, potential customers, and more. Users can also access articles, quick startup advice, and contact the developer for 1 on 1 help.

name: Image AI App
description: The Image AI App is an AI image generator that creates images such as D&D characters, Pokemon, dragons, anime, cartoon characters, art, and more.

name: Durable
description: A website generator powered by AI that allows users to create a fully designed website with copy, images, and a contact form in under a minute. It also includes AI copywriting, SEO, analytics, and a simple CRM, all with one login. Additionally, it offers a library of professional images and icons and AI-generated ideas for naming a business.

name: WritingMate
description: WritingMate.ai is a Chrome browser extension that helps users draft or reply to emails or messages, generate blog posts, essays, or other personal content, create marketing copy, press releases, or other work content, write faster and fix grammar, rewrite, and translate on the go, and research more effectively with summarization, brainstorming, and questions.

name: AiSofiya
description: Sofiya is an AI-powered text to speech converter that can quickly and accurately synthesize text into natural-sounding speech in over 135 languages and dialects. It supports multiple audio formats and frequencies, and has a powerful sound studio to merge and enhance audio results. It is a versatile tool that can be used for customer service chatbots, voice assistants, educational chatbots, text generation for natural language processing tasks and more.

name: Civitai
description: Civitai is an online platform that makes it easy for people to share and discover resources for creating AI art. Users can upload and share models that have been trained to generate art in a particular style, or browse and download models created by other users. Civitai also provides a vibrant and supportive community of AI artists, where users can exchange ideas and share their experiences.

name: Teachable Machine
description: Teachable Machine is a web-based tool that enables users to create machine learning models quickly and easily, without any coding required. It is flexible, allowing users to use files or capture examples live. It can be used to classify images, audio, and poses, and the models created can be exported for use in sites, apps, and more.

name: Tute.ai
description: Tute.AI is a virtual tutoring platform powered by the GPT language model. It provides tailored teaching tailored to the user's needs using AI, with the aim of guiding users to the future of learning.

name: Pollinations
description: Pollinations is an engine that uses algorithms to create personalized AI media. It offers applications such as an NFT series generator, Busy Bee Social Media Bot, and Pollinations Studio for commissioned works. It also has technology for generating immersive landscapes and 3D avatars with text or voice prompts. The ecosystem is open-source and rewards contributors.

name: MeetGeek
description: MeetGeek is an AI meeting assistant that helps users maximize the value of their meetings. It automatically records, transcribes, summarizes, and provides highlights and keywords from meetings. It also provides meeting insights, workflows and integrations, custom branding and pricing solutions, and multi-language support. MeetGeek can be used for customer calls, team meetings, training and onboarding, interviews, and online classes.

name: Vacay
description: Vacation & Travel Chat Assistant. This AI-Assistant can design a custom trip, give you inspiration on where to go, and even generate local recommendations for hotels, restaurants, and attractions.

name: Valideo
description: Valideo is an AI-powered Amazon product recommendation platform that provides users with personalized product recommendations based on their individual preferences and needs. It has a user-friendly interface and saves time and money, and has been praised for its accuracy and efficiency.

name: Brainfish
description: Brainfish is an AI-powered knowledgebase platform that provides customers with quick and relevant answers to their questions, while also improving help articles with proofreading and suggestions. It enables businesses to easily migrate their existing knowledgebase in under 5 minutes, with multi-language support and analytics to better understand customer needs.

name: Hot Reach AI
description: This tool is designed to help increase response rates for cold emails. It takes LinkedIn profile URLs and automatically generates personalized first lines. The process only takes a couple minutes, and any credits are refunded if the tool is unable to generate a first line.

name: AI Reality
description: AI Reality is a platform that allows users to create simple web AR prototypes using AI technology. It uses Stable Diffusion and Open AI to generate augmented reality, and is constantly updated to improve processing and understanding. It provides an easy way to learn and practice creating AR experiences.
pricing_model: Price Unknown / Product Not Launched Yet

name: Slite - Ask
description: Slite's new AI assistant – Ask – answers questions based on your team's documentation. Take the pain out of finding info, learning from the past, and getting new team mates up to speed. Have a question? Just ask.
pricing_model: Price Unknown / Product Not Launched Yet

name: StoriesForKids.ai
description: StoriesForKids.ai is a tool that helps parents and children create stories and illustrations together. It provides unlimited access to stories, poems, and beautiful illustrations, as well as the ability to save and share creations. It works on all phones and tablets and different pricing options are available.

name: Begone, Spammer
description: BeGone Spammer is a tool that generates AI-generated replies to unsolicited emails. It is designed to help users assert dominance over their inboxes and outwit spammers.

name: Pixela.ai
description: The above tool allows users to upload images generated by a Stable Diffusion Algorithm to share with the community. The tool also allows users to find random textures.

name: GlowAI
description: The above tool is an AI-powered skincare routine generator. It allows users to input their budget, skin type, and top skin concerns in order to generate a personalized skincare routine tailored to their needs.

name: Public Prompts
description: A large and growing list of freely available image prompts. Don't buy prompts... Grab them for free. The site also includes examples from various models and embeddings.

name: Neeva
description: Neeva is a private search engine and browser that is 100% ad-free and never sells or shares members' data with any third party. It offers two plans for members to choose between, a Free Basic membership and a paid, Premium membership. The Free Basic plan is completely free and full-featured, allowing members to search both the web and connected personal accounts like Gmail or Dropbox, set news and shopping preferences, and search from multiple devices. Neeva also offers a Premium membership that includes unlimited searches and privacy-protecting tools like a Premium Password Manager and VPN. Neeva is available for both iOS and Android devices, and its browser extension is compatible with all major browsers.

name: giftassistant.io
description: GiftAssistant.io is an AI-powered tool that helps users quickly find gift ideas for any occasion. It requires no registration or data storage and will generate ideas in seconds. The tool also provides easy links to purchase the suggested items.

name: Happy Mama
description: HappyMama is a tool that provides instant answers to pregnancy questions.

name: MotionIt AI
description: MotionIt.ai creates professional slides & videos for pitch decks, conference presentations & more. Simple steps, export to Google Slides, PowerPoint & PDF

name: Predict
description: Predict is an AI-powered predictive tool that helps businesses increase conversions and improve creatives on the fly. It leverages consumer neuroscience data from eye tracking and brain responses studies to generate heatmaps, cognitive scores, and industry benchmarks, enabling companies to pre-test creatives, compare to benchmarks, and conduct unlimited testing.
pricing_model: Price Unknown / Product Not Launched Yet

name: Taskade
description: Taskade is a collaborative productivity tool that enables teams to plan, organize, and execute their projects. It features dynamic views such as List, Board, Calendar, Action, Mind Map, Org Chart, and Smart Project View. Taskade integrates with popular calendar services, including Apple Mail, Google Calendar, and Outlook. It also offers a wide range of customizable templates, collaboration features, cloud integration, version history, and global search.

name: Heyday
description: Heyday is an AI-powered memory assistant that helps people remember more of what they learn while browsing the web. It automatically saves pages you visit and resurfaces them alongside search results, documents, messages, files, newsletters, notes, presentations, spreadsheets, tweets, and more. Heyday is a secure and private product and can be added to a browser with a fast and easy setup.

name: Deep Dream Generator
description: Deep Dream Generator is a team of techies and creatives on a mission to revolutionize the way users generate images. The AI-powered product enables users to quickly and easily generate unique and high-quality images with just a few pointers. It offers tools such as Text 2 Dream, Deep Style, and Deep Dream, which use a combination of text prompts, base images, and deep learning to create art, photorealistic images, and psychedelic and abstract art.

name: MealsAI
description: MealsAI is a tool that helps create unique recipes from any ingredients or dietary restrictions. It can generate recipes quickly and easily, and provides festive and holiday-ready recipes. Users can share recipes with friends and browse recipes created by others around the world.

name: Narration Box
description: Narration Box is a voice synthesis service that enables users to create voiceovers, narrations, audiobooks, audio pages, podcasts, and more. It features more than 700 AI-enhanced human-like narrators in over 20 languages, a power-packed speech editor, and audio widgets for blogs and news sites. It also includes resources such as FAQs, feedback, updates, and more. It is free to get started and provides tools for distribution, analytics, monetization, and more.

name: ChatBotKit
description: ChatBotKit is a platform that provides tools and services to create and manage advanced AI chat bots. It offers features such as custom datasets, custom skillsets, Slack and widget integration, GPT-3.5 support, content moderation, semantic search, no-code platform, simple pricing, and extreme customization. There is also a monthly membership program that includes access to any chatbot and all of its features.

name: Sale Whale
description: SaleWhale is a fast-growing tech company that provides AI sales rep solutions to businesses. Their chatbots are designed to handle customer inquiries, provide personalized recommendations, and close sales in real-time. They also offer customer support bots to ensure clients understand how to use a product or service. SaleWhale offers a base integration fee and monthly subscription, and can provide custom features on request.

name: VoiceType
description: VoiceType is a Chrome browser extension that helps users write emails quickly and easily. It uses AI to generate emails based on verbal descriptions provided by the user. It is designed to help those who struggle with writing emails, or those who simply want to be more productive. It also has features such as speech recognition, so it can understand different accents, and the ability to tailor emails to specific conversations.

name: Present AI
description: A tool that allows users to create amazing presentations 10X faster with AI. It offers a variety of options to generate images, including low poly, cyberpunk, surrealism, anime, realism, memphis design, fantasy, and cartoon.

name: Lexii.ai
description:
Lexii is an AI search assistant that can answer questions. Lexii was created to provide users with accurate, up-to-date information from reliable sources. Lexii is powered by ChatGPT, a natural language processing technology. Lexii is designed to provide users with a comprehensive, balanced, and objective assessment of topics.
ChatGPT is not always reliable, so it is best used as a guide rather than a source of definitive information. Lexii, on the other hand, is powered by ChatGPT but also has access to real-time information and the ability to cite sources. This makes Lexii a more reliable source of information than ChatGPT.

name: AI ChatLab
description: AI ChatLab is an AI toolkit app that provides users with access to the latest and most advanced AI chatbots, all in one convenient and ad-free app. It features ChatGPT 3.5, YouChat, Perplexity AI, and Neeva, which is a privacy-focused search engine. It is user-friendly and offers a wide range of features such as language translation, question answering, text generation, and on-demand answers to any questions.

name: Pattern Cafe
description: Cutting-edge AI technology generates new and one-of-a-kind patterns for fabric, gift wrap, wallpaper, and game textures. Whether you're a professional designer or a hobbyist, the user-friendly platform makes it easy to explore and create a wide range of designs.

name: WatchNow
description: WatchNow AI is the first app that uses ChatGPT to find your next binge-worthy movie or show. Simply add a few titles that you like and get 10 hyper-tailored recommendations.

name: Adaptiv Academy
description: Ada, the AI-powered mentor on Adaptiv can answer career-related questions and help you discover the most relevant career paths based on your strengths and interests, and provide guidance on how to prepare for different careers by suggesting courses.

name: MagicSlides App
description: Create Presentation Slides with AI in seconds, Choose your title and number of slides, and MagicSlides will take care of the rest! Get the perfect presentation ready in no time. Additionally you can provide content which you want to be included in the presentation to get more personalized presentations.

name: Stork.ai
description: Stork is a collaboration workspace for hybrid and remote teams that allows them to work asynchronously aided by Artificial Professionals. It provides features such as recording calls, voice and video notes, channels for team alignment, watercoolers for serendipitous meetings and a built-in screen recorder to share video stories. It also provides read and playback receipts for all messages, video, and audio conferences.

name: Superflow Rewrite
description: Superflow is a next-generation website review tool built for modern web agencies. It allows users to add rich media annotations on live websites, generate copy using ChatGPT, manage tasks, record, and share for review. It also integrates with other tools such as Clickup, Webflow, Asana, and Slack.

name: TTS-Voice-Wizard
description: TTS Voice Wizard is a tool that enables users to convert their speech to text, and then back to speech, through Microsoft Azure Voice Recognition and TTS. It also sends OSC messages to VRChat to display text on an avatar. The tool has a number of customization options, including 100+ different voices, 20+ supported languages, and the ability to show a song title, artist, and progress above the user.

name: EmailMagic AI
description: EmailMagic is the AI assistant that helps you write emails 10x faster. Let it be Your Digital Twin. It Writes Emails Just Like You!

name: OneTone.ai
description: OneTone.ai is a browser extension that helps customer support agents save time and reduce typing errors by predicting the right sentences and phrases they need to use. It uses AI to learn and personalize according to the user's responses, and can be installed within a minute.

name: Blog Post Generator
description: The above tool is a post generator that allows you to choose an industry and generate a blog post related to that industry. It also creates a titles, cites sources, and writes a meta description for the post.

name: Image Cleaner
description: ImgCleaner is a free image cleanup tool that uses the latest AI technology to instantly remove unwanted objects from images and pictures. It can clean up people, scratches, graffiti, watermarks, and text, and it can also retouch pictures for commercial use. The tool is 100% free and privacy safe, and it also provides seamless object removal experience.

name: GPT2Markdown
description: The GPT2Markdown extension is a tool that allows users to export their conversations with ChatGPT in a single click, in Markdown format. The extension also has a feature that uses ChatGPT's auto-labelling to name files, and it is open-source. The tool can be used to store the exported conversations in a digital tool like Notion or in a dedicated folder on an external hard drive. The source code for the tool is available on GitHub and the tool requests only bare minimum permissions and does not collect any user data.

name: Extrapolate
description: Extrapolate is a free and privacy-friendly tool that allows users to upload a photo and see how they will look at different ages in the future

name: Neural Love
description: Allows you to generate images for free, upscale images and videos, outpaint, train Dream-booth models, colorize videos and photos and more

name: Midjourney Grid Splitter
description: Use the MJSplitter to split your Midjourney Grid into single images.

name: ViralViews
description: ViralViews is an AI-powered tool that provides daily content on specific industries across social media and other platforms. It offers a range of plans for individuals, small teams, agencies, and businesses, and allows users to customize their feeds. It also provides a daily trend report and premium support.

name: AI Screenwriting Tool
description: AIScreenwriter is an AI-powered screenwriting tool designed to help screenwriters quickly brainstorm, structure, and write their stories. It provides valuable insights and suggestions from the AI, and the first 300 users to sign up receive 2,500 free tokens. The tool allows users to edit their screenplay as they type, and supercharges creativity.

name: NovelAI
description: NovelAI is a monthly subscription service that uses Artificial Intelligence algorithms to create human-like writing based on a user's input. It offers features such as image generation, text adventure module, customizable editor, secure writing, AI modules, and a Lorebook.

name: Quickie
description: Quickie is an AI-powered extension that allows users to generate text-to-speech, summarizer, expander, tweeter, lyrics, and other features. It also offers custom quickies that allow users to build their own shortcuts with prompts and inputs. Quickie is free forever with 1 quickie per credit, and there are paid plans with unlimited quickies, saved results, and unlimited custom quickies.

name: Wiz.chat
description: Wizchat is a tool that adds GPT-3 capabilities to Slack workspaces. It allows users to ask questions and summarize content from URLs by simply mentioning @Wizchat and typing in their prompt.

name: ChefGPT
description: An AI-powered recipe recommendation tool that helps you to never worry about what's for dinner again. It suggests recipes based on the ingredients and tools you have, and the time you have available. It has two Chef Modes, Gourmet Mode which uses only the best combinations of ingredients and All-In Mode which uses all ingredients listed.

name: zenen.ai
description: Zenen is an AI assistant that helps with creative and storytelling tasks. It is able to engage in conversations and provide answers to questions related to history, poetry, books, places, and more. It can also provide summaries of books, advice, and poems, as well as offer creative nudge when needed. Speak in voice commands and get results from ChatGPT.
pricing_model: Price Unknown / Product Not Launched Yet

name: StockGPT
description:
StockGPT is an AI-powered search tool that uses Tesla's quarterly earnings call transcripts dating back to Q2 2011 to help users search for specific information from a given quarter or year. The tool provides users with more accurate and up-to-date information than manual searches, and it comes with a list of examples to help users get started.
Note from Matt: This tool is solely focused on Tesla's stock at the moment

name: AiTax
description: AiTax is an AI-based tax-preparation software that helps entrepreneurs file their taxes with accuracy and efficiency while avoiding mistakes, increasing any potential refund and avoiding an unnecessary audit. The software uses Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning Technology to provide a secure filing process with a money-back guarantee, audit protection and in-court legal defense. Customers have praised the software for its ease of use, great results and knowledge of tax law.
pricing_model: Price Unknown / Product Not Launched Yet

name: Paraphrasing Tool
description:
AI Writing Assistant by paraphrasingtool.ai is all in one writing platform for writers. It generates, essays, stories, articles and translate documents. It also offers built-in research panel to find only web sources and paraphrases, summarize or cite them in the editor.
Note From Matt: There are a ton of ads the I feel really ruin the user-experience. Be aware. (personal opinion)

name: WordfixerBot
description: WordfixerBot is an AI writing assistant tool that ultilizes AI technology to provide text paraphrasing, grammar checking, and summarization capabilities. WordfixerBot is designed to help you improve your written communication, whether it be for business, academic, or personal use.

name: WordAi
description: WordAi is an AI-powered content rewriting tool that allows users to quickly generate unique, high-quality content. It uses advanced machine learning models to rewrite sentences and phrases, adding LSI keywords and optimizing for readability. WordAi also makes it easy to bulk rewrite articles, add rewriting to any workflow, and export rewrites in bulk.

name: Compose AI
description: Compose AI is a Chrome extension that helps users save time on writing by providing AI-powered autocompletion and text generation. It comes with features such as autocompletion, rephrasing, shortcuts, and compose emails from natural language instruction. It also offers personalized writing styles, contextually aware suggestions, and a self-improving AI to automate writing. The plugin is free to use, and there is a premium version with some advanced features.

name: InstantArt
description: Unlock the full potential of AI art with InstantArt! With unlimited image generation, over 25 fine-tuned stable diffusion models.

name: CopyPro
description: CopyPro is a cloud-based copywriting platform that offers users access to templates and resources from some of the world's top copywriters and marketers. It provides AI-driven tools and features to help users quickly create, customize, and optimize copy for their business. It includes a template library, a project manager, an AI-based template editor, a marketing blueprint creator, an AI Rewrite™, an AI-Based Copy Impact Score™, and email support. CopyPro also offers three different membership levels, with the highest level providing live group coaching, lead acquisition training, one-on-one customization and training, personalized funnel creation, and Jon Benson's Hook System.

name: Meet Millie
description: Meet Millie is an AI-powered tool that helps users to get the best response rate on dating apps. It provides personalized pick-up artist skills, such as a pick up line, poem, best date, best photos, bio writing, and finish my sentence features. It helps users to break the ice, surprise their match, and get deeper conversations and relevant dates.

name: Evoke
description: Evoke is a cloud-based AI hosting and inferencing service that provides users with access to a wide range of AI models for image and art generation. With Evoke, users can deploy their own AI models and pay only for the use of the service. Evoke provides direct customer support, unlimited usage, and flexible infrastructure for scalability.

name: Jenni AI
description: Jenni is an AI writing assistant that helps writers create content 10x faster. It has powerful features such as AI autocomplete, plagiarism-free content, in-text citations, and paraphrasing. It can be used for writing blog posts, essays, emails, personal statements, stories, and speeches. It is available on desktop and has a built-in plagiarism checker.

name: Img Upscaler
description: ImgUpscaler is a free tool that allows users to quickly and easily upscale images using the latest AI technology. It offers batch processing and the potential to improve the quality of images without sacrificing resolution. It is optimized for upscaling Anime and Cartoon photos for use as wallpapers, and is more effective than open-source programs like Waifu2x. ImgUpscaler ensures privacy by clearing photos within 24 hours, and provides free weekly credits for users.

name: Tiledesk
description: Chatbot Design Studio is an all-in-one customer engagement platform that helps businesses build, deploy, and manage chatbots and live chat widgets on multiple channels, including WhatsApp, Facebook Messenger, and websites. It features adaptive multichannel chatbot design, conversational ticketing, unified messaging, and mobile apps. It also allows businesses to create custom chatbot templates with its no-code open source chatbot builder.

name: Tweetmonk
description: Tweetmonk is a smart Twitter thread editor powered by AI that helps businesses and individuals automate and grow their Twitter accounts. It provides an easy-to-use editor with a simple interface that is smart at the same time and helps make content more engaging and conversion-friendly with AI tools. It also provides powerful analytics to analyze engagement metrics and improve content and increase growth, as well as AI-powered tools to make tweets standout. With Tweetmonk users can also write and schedule tweets and threads, generate relevant hashtags, get inspired by examples of popular tweets, queue content in seconds, and boost their content with one-click scheduling.

name: Midjourney Prompt Generator
description: The Midjourney Prompt Generator is a web application that generates prompts based on a text input and various options. It allows users to customize their prompts with mediums, art movements, rendering engines, materials, cameras, filters, scenes, chaos, seeds, image weight, height, quality, width, aspect ratio, version, stylization, uplight, beta, HD, and same seed.

name: Prompt Silo
description: A database of MidJourney prompts with a prompt builder. You can select all of your MidJourney prompt settings and pick from styles, artists, topics, and more to craft the perfect prompts for your needs. And it's totally free to use and generates amazing results.

name: Releasenote.ai
description: Release Notes Simplified with GPT-3. Keep your customers and company up to date with the amazing value you shipped. Just add few details and let AI generate your first draft.

name: Genmo
description: Genmo is a platform for creating and sharing interactive, immersive generative art. Go beyond 2D images on Genmo by creating videos, 3D scenes, animations, vector design assets and more.
pricing_model: Price Unknown / Product Not Launched Yet

name: Kaiber
description: Kaiber is a video generation engine that enables users to create videos from their own images or text description. It offers features such as Spotify Canvas for musicians, inspiration for artists, content for creators, and fun for futurists, allowing them to express themselves in a unique way and push the bounds of AI tools. Kaiber is free to use and requires no credit card.

name: Image Mixer
description: The above tool is a Stable Diffusion Image Variations model that has been fine-tuned to take multiple CLIP image embeddings as inputs, allowing users to combine the image embeddings from multiple images to mix their concepts and add text concepts for greater variation. The output is a 640x640 image and it can be run locally or on Lambda GPU Cloud.

name: Pickaxe
description: Pickaxe is an AI-powered tool that allows anyone to quickly create tools without any coding required. It also provides a platform for users to discover existing AI tools, as well as collaborate and share with the Pickaxe community.

name: SheetAI
description: SheetAI is a Google Workspace Add-on that unlocks the power of AI for your spreadsheets. SheetAI enables users to automate data analysis, get answers from data, generate images, and generate Sheets formulas with AI, allowing them to make better decisions and save time.

name: Anote
description: Anote is a powerful AI-assisted data labeling platform that accelerates the labeling process for unstructured text data. It uses few shot learning to label data with minimal amounts of labeled examples, and leverages state-of-the-art transformer models to achieve high accuracy with a shorter labeling time than traditional methods. It also provides explainability features, allowing users to better understand their model's performance. Anote is designed to be cost-effective, flexible and help to create high quality data for AI use cases.

name: Clips AI
description: Clips AI is a tool that helps creators repurpose long-form video or audio content into social media clips and distribute them to social media. It uses AI to predict which clips will get the most engagement and also makes it easy to upload, create, and select clips. It also offers custom branding and team collaboration features. The tool is currently in alpha testing and there is a waitlist for the closed beta.

name: PowerPen
description: PowerPen AI Paraphrasing Tool is a comprehensive text editing tool that allows users to easily alter the language style, tone, and length of any text, while providing grammar, spelling, and punctuation checking capabilities. It can be used to compose responses to emails, tweets, and other social media messages, as well as to summarize long pieces of text.

name: SkimIt.ai
description: SkimIt is an AI-powered tool that allows users to quickly get summaries of any article by emailing a link to go@skimit.ai. It also provides drafts of shareable tweets and a LinkedIn post to easily share the summary with friends. The summaries are generated by OpenAI's GPT technology and are not guaranteed to be accurate. The data stored by SkimIt is limited to the email address that sent the request, any CC'd email addresses, and the first URL sent within the email.

name: Vowel
description: Vowel AI's automated meeting summaries allow users to save time on admin work and keep everyone on the same page. Record meetings in Vowel and the AI-powered summary will be the first thing you see in the Home tab. Review, edit, and copy/paste to share with others, or click on a past recorded meeting from the dashboard to instantly review the summary alongside the transcript, recording, and notes.

name: Decktopus
description: This is a free AI-generated prompt template that helps you create captivating product launch copy. It helps you craft content and write engaging launch copy with ease. The template contains suggested questions and answers that you can use to create your own unique product launch copy. It also helps you to create a story and a voice for your product launch.

name: Deep Anime
description: Deep Anime is a powerful app that allows users to transform any photo into a stunning anime scene. It uses advanced artificial intelligence to automatically detect faces and objects in the photo, then applies a variety of transforming neural networks to create a unique and dynamic look.

It supports over 27 languages and has a browser addon for Chrome and Firefox. With Corrector App, you can check for misspellings, grammatical mistakes, and punctuation errors, as well as receive word suggestions to make your text sound better.

name: GiftasticAI
description: Giftastic.AI is a personalized gift recommendation engine that uses cutting-edge AI technology to analyze the personal characteristics of the person and recommend unique and thoughtful gifts. It is free of charge, and helps users quickly and easily find the perfect gift for their loved ones.

name: Text GPT
description: With TextGPT you can easily access OpenAi’s GPT and Dall-E 2 through text messaging, receiving quick and accurate answers to any question you may have and generating realistic images with a simple text.

name: Free AI Detector
description: Insert your content and let it scan for AI-generated content. Results will be more reliable with at least 25 words.

name: SEO.ai
description: SEO.ai is an AI platform that helps SEO marketers create high-quality SEO content faster and ensure it will perform. It offers a range of features, such as keyword research, advanced SEO score, content suggestions, competitor benchmarks, real-time SEO guidance, and AI-assisted copywriting. It works in over 50 languages and offers a free trial with 10,000 A.I. words and 10 A.I. reports.

name: Trudo
description: The tool provides an intuitive user interface for training, testing, and deploying OpenAI models using CSV files. Users are able to select one of OpenAI's four models and view pricing before fine-tuning, and then simply click start to begin the fine-tuning process. Once the process is complete, users can test and share their models with a link.

name: AssemblyAI
description: Automatically convert audio and video files and live audio streams to text with AssemblyAI's Speech-to-Text APIs. Do more with Audio Intelligence - summarization, content moderation, topic detection, and more. Powered by cutting-edge AI models.

name: DiscuroAI
description: Discuro is an all-in-one platform for developers looking to quickly and easily build and test complex AI work-flows. With Discuro, users can define their work-flows in an easy-to-use UI, and then make one API call to execute their work-flows. Discuro also enables users to monitor AI usage across work-flows and add meta-data to build bigger data-sets. This allows users to better understand how their customers are using AI apps and find opportunities for optimisation.

name: MonkeyLearn
description: MonkeyLearn is a no-code text analytics platform that helps businesses quickly analyze and visualize customer feedback. With pre-built and custom machine learning models, and business templates tailored for different scenarios, MonkeyLearn enables users to quickly gain insights from their text data and take actionable steps to improve their products, customer satisfaction, and customer experience.

name: re:tune
description: The tool provided is a platform to help people build GPT-3 powered applications without writing any code. It provides a rich playground to train AI models, monetization of data and fine-tuned models, and the ability to create chatbots, personal assistants, and more.

name: Explain Like I'm Five
description: Explain Like I'm Five (ELI5) is a website that simplifies complex topics using AI so that even a child can understand them. Users can select a specific topic and choose how dumbed-down they want the explanation to be, ranging from "really dumb" to "really smart". This allows users to get the answers they need without having to learn anything. ELI5 provides a wide variety of topics, making it easy, fun, and efficient to pretend to understand anything.

name: Waymark
description: Waymark is a video production tool that helps businesses create high-impact ads quickly and easily. It allows users to import business information, which is then used by AI to generate a video based on their brand. The video can be finalized with any last adjustments, and is built to be aired on TV, CTV, and digital platforms.

name: Tweet Hunter
description: Tweet Hunter is an all-in-one Twitter growth and monetization tool that helps you build a highly-engaged and relevant audience, drive sales, and get more clients and subscribers. With Tweet Hunter, you can find content ideas, write faster and better, automate tasks to save time, engage with people and build relationships, and analyze your performance. Features include a library of 3M+ viral tweets, AI-powered writing and rewriting, automated messaging, Twitter CRM, and detailed analytics.

name: Upstream AI
description: Upstream is a Chrome Extension that lets users easily run GPT on any website. It does the usual things like writing about a topic, summarizing and simplifying content, the difference is that it gathers context automatically from your Chrome tabs.

name: ChatGPT for Siri
description: This tool allows users to activate ChatGPT through Siri using voice commands. It prompts the user to ask a question, sends it to ChatGPT, reads the answer, and allows the user to save the answer into a new Apple Note. The user can setup the tool by copying their ChatGPT API key and adding it to the designated placeholder in the shortcut.

name: We Made a Story
description: Generate original children's bedtime stories with the help of Artificial Intelligence Simply write your idea in a sentence or two, and let the AI do the rest! It generates the story, the pictures and the audio narration for your kids to listen to as they drift away to sleep

name: AILab Tools
description: AILabTools provides a range of image processing tools, including AI Photo Colorize, Image Erasure, Photo to Painting, Cartoon Yourself, Change Facial Expressions, Age & Gender Swap, Face Filters, Face Blur, Retouch Portraits, Hairstyle Changer, Universal Background Remover, Head Extraction, and Image Upscaler. These tools allow users to enhance, edit and retouch photos and images, as well as to create cartoon avatars, remove unwanted objects and texts, and perform age and gender swaps. AILabTools also provides API support.

name: STUDIO
description: Studio's first release is an AI-augmented design app for creating modern websites. It comes with a powerful experience unlike any other: Highlight an area you are stuck on. Marvel as design suggestions appear before your eyes. Speak to it. Watch as multi-step tasks autocomplete themselves. Press one button. Observe as your design adapts to fit all screen sizes.
pricing_model: Price Unknown / Product Not Launched Yet

name: Synthesys X
description: Synthesys X is a Google Chrome extension that can generate new images based on the objects and patterns detected in a given image, considering their similarities and relevance.

name: Digital First AI
description: Digital First AI is a marketing automation platform that helps businesses create and execute marketing plans in seconds with the help of AI. It offers personalized business tactics recommendations based on data and provides access to a library of tactics, strategies of popular brands, and experienced marketers. It can help businesses save up to 5-10X time, increase revenue in hours, generate content 10X faster, and get permanent growth recommendations. It also provides other features such as task assignments to team members, organic ways of improving traction and revenue, and finding new sources of income.

name: Prezo
description: Prezo is a tool that combines artificial intelligence with presentation creation to help users create engaging and dynamic presentations. It offers features such as automated design, one-click transitions, and AI-powered image optimization.

name: Dreamily
description: Dreamily is a creative AI companion that helps you create stories, worlds, and characters. It offers collaborative writing models, sentence length preferences, and the ability to share stories as images. You can also create your own unique universe, including story backgrounds, character entries, and inter-character relationships, which Dreamily remembers and helps you complete.

name: AI Social Bio
description: AI Social Bio is an automated tool that helps users create custom social media bios, tailored to their interests and goals. It allows users to add keywords to shape their bio, as well as choose inspiring influencers to model their bio after. The tool also allows users to A/B test their bios.

name: Bannerbear
description: Bannerbear is a tool that helps automate and scale marketing efforts. It offers an API and integrations for generating images, videos, PDFs, and more for social media visuals, ecommerce banners, and other marketing tasks.

name: GPT-2 Output Detector
description: A simple free tool where you can plug in text from the web and see if it was generated with GPT-2. It's not specifically designed for newer tools that leverage GPT-3 but seemingly still does a pretty good job of detecting it anyway.

name: AIHelperBot
description: AIHelperBot is a tool that helps individuals and companies generate accurate and efficient SQL queries quickly and boost their productivity. It allows users to add custom database schemas with few clicks, use autosuggest with custom table and column names to generate queries, and save generated queries as snippets. It supports PostgreSQL, Oracle, MSSQL, MySQL, BigQuery, and MariaDB.

name: PeopleAI
description: People AI allows users to converse with and learn from some of the most influential and significant figures in human history. It features a library of notable figures from the past, including Mahatma Gandhi, Martin Luther King Jr., Albert Einstein, Nelson Mandela, Queen Elizabeth II, and many more. Users can also contribute to the library by submitting information about new people for inclusion.

name: PromptLayer
description: PromptLayer is a platform that allows users to track and manage their GPT prompt engineering. It acts as a middleware between code and OpenAI’s python library, recording all OpenAI API requests and allowing users to search and explore their request history in the PromptLayer dashboard. To use PromptLayer, users need to create an account and generate an API key. PromptLayer can then be installed using pip and used with OpenAI APIs with an additional argument of pl_tags, allowing users to track and group requests in the dashboard.

name: Codeium
description: Codeium is a programming superpower that enables developers to quickly make changes to unfamiliar languages and codebases using natural language. It also helps minimize boilerplate coding, find and use APIs, and generate unit tests. It supports Python, CSS, JavaScript, Java, and Regex.

name: Magician for Figma
description: Magician is a design tool for Figma powered by AI that enables users to design with the power of AI for copywriting, generating unique icons from text, automating tasks, and prototyping with code. It works alongside users to expand their creativity and imagination through its Magic Spells feature.

name: ContentIn
description: ContentIn is an all-in-one suit for LinkedIn content creation. It helps users write engaging content by providing templates, AI Idea Generator, AI Writer, and post analytics. ContentIn also allows users to schedule posts, add media, manage ideas, and rework successful posts.

name: ExplainThis.AI
description: ExplainThis AI is a text generation library with pre-trained language models that provides users with an AI assistant to help them understand and digest long pages. It can explain concepts in plain language and provide a summary of the entire page with a single click.
pricing_model: Price Unknown / Product Not Launched Yet

name: MarketingBlocks AI

description: ‘Human-like’ All-In-One AI Marketing Assistant that writes, creates & designs all your landing pages, promo videos, ads, marketing copy, graphics, email swipes, voiceovers, blog posts, articles, art & more in minutes.

name: SuenaGringo
description:
This tool helps spanish speaking immigrants generate natural sounding and professional translations with just a few clicks! Choose from a variety of different literary tones and formats for a personalized experience. Immigrating is already a difficult endeavor, and not knowing english can slow you down greatly. We are trying to break down the language barrier for people who want to communicate with their boss, their childrens' teachers, potential and existing clients, etc. You can try our free version for 24 hours and see it in action.
Note: Site is in Spanish

name: Targum Video
description: Targumbeta is a tool that translates social media videos from any language to any language in a matter of seconds. It automatically detects the language of the video, transcribes and translates it, and then hosts it. It also features trending videos on its homepage and enables users to share videos on social media platforms.

name: Uminal
description: Like ChatGPT but can also search the web

name: You.com
description: You.com is an AI-powered search engine that helps users learn, work faster, and write with AI. It includes 150+ apps to personalize search results, as well as features like private search and a multi-dimensional interface for faster discovery. YouChat is also available for users to talk with.

name: Sense
description: Sense is a self-organised space that provides teams with a single source of truth for all their projects. It automatically connects, organises and syncs data from multiple apps in order to provide useful insights, increased capacity growth, higher onboarding speed and more successful cases. It offers a flexible structure, so teams can choose what data structure works best for them.
